> We add a comment header [#11205 (comment)](https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/issues/11205#issuecomment-680594689) with meta information.

What do you mean by that? The comment says *we could add*&hellip;

By the English grammar (*We drink tea every morning*), it looks like we added it every day, only to be undone overnight, hence no progress ☹
